title: Top US officials hold first in-person meeting with the Taliban since the US killed al Qaeda's leader in July

title: Surveillance footage captures moment of explosion
description: Surveillance footage from cameras on the Kerch bridge leading to Russian-annexed Crimea shows the moment of a large explosion on the roadway.
